=head1 NAME

  vzconfig - GUI fron-end for vzctl(server virtualization solution)

=head1 SYNOPSIS
       
  vzconfig [OPTION]...

=head1 DESCRIPTION

  vzconfig - it`s GUI fron-end for vzctl based on bash script 
  and used ncurses utilities for displays user-friendly dialog
  boxes from shell scripts.

=head1 OPTIONS

  If you do not use OPTION, then run GUI.

  -C "command"

    Command executed in all VE. With this option, vzconfig use 
    VZEXCLUDE variable for exluded VE.

  -C2 

    Command executed in all VE and on host system. With this option, vzconfig use 
    VZEXCLUDE variable for exluded VE.

  --help

    display this help and exit

  --version

    output version information and exit

